ch&q;:&q;Advanced search filter that has to be used to filter the result set, with syntax `&l;:filter-name&g;,&l;:filter-operator&g;=&l;:filter-value&g;`. Not URL encoded. For example `author,authority=5df05073-3be7-410d-8166-e254369e4166` or `title,contains=sample text`&q;,&q;process.param.description-h.metadata-export-search&q;:&q;help&q;,&q;process.param.description-f.metadata-import&q;:&q;source file&q;,&q;process.param.description-s.metadata-import&q;:&q;silent operation - doesn&s;t request confirmation of changes USE WITH CAUTION&q;,&q;process.param.description-w.metadata-import&q;:&q;workflow - when adding new items, use collection workflow&q;,&q;process.param.description-n.metadata-import&q;:&q;notify - when adding new items using a workflow, send notification emails&q;,&q;process.param.description-v.metadata-import&q;:&q;validate - just validate the csv, don&s;t run the import&q;,&q;process.param.description-t.metadata-import&q;:&q;template - when adding new items, use the collection template (if it exists)&q;,&q;process.param.description-h.metadata-import&q;:&q;help&q;,&q;process.param.description-l.orcid-bulk-pull&q;:&q;to simulates the callback only for linked profiles&q;,&q;process.param.description-f.orcid-bulk-push&q;:&q;force the synchronization ignoring maximum attempts&q;,&q;process.param.description-h.process-cleaner&q;:&q;help&q;,&q;process.param.description-r.process-cleaner&q;:&q;delete the process with RUNNING status&q;,&q;process.param.description-f.process-cleaner&q;:&q;delete the process with FAILED status&q;,&q;process.param.description-c.process-cleaner&q;:&q;delete the process with COMPLETED status (default if no statuses are specified)&q;,&q;process.param.description-a.retry-tracker&q;:&q;Add a new \&q;failed\&q; row to the table with a url (test purposes only)&q;,&q;process.param.description-r.retry-tracker&q;:&q;Retry sending requests to all urls stored in the table with failed requests. This includes the url that can be added through